Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:25.77,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur13.5\fad(484,484)\fsp1.35}通过呼吸交换的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:39.10,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur13.5\fad(484,484)\fsp1.35}就算没有形状也能传达到心中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:50.78,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur13.5\fad(484,484)\fsp1.35}静静地感受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:55.65,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur13.5\fad(484,484)\fsp1.35}在黄昏所停息的脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:59.59,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur13.5\fad(484,484)\fsp1.35}我寻找着明天的路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:07.44,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur13.5\fad(484,484)\fsp1.35}一步一步  和你步幅合拍
