Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:45.98,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur13.5\fad(484,484)\fsp1.35}就算再也听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:21:02.52,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur13.5\fad(484,484)\fsp1.35}用能微笑面对所有人的容颜去编织吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:10.80,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur13.5\fad(484,484)\fsp1.35}For you…
